Reasoning: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses various machine learning techniques for state representation learning and compares their performance with end-to-end learning. 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on using reinforcement learning to control real robots and evaluates the effectiveness of different state representation learning methods on goal-based robotics tasks. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper mentions using vision to control real robots and the challenges associated with it. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper discusses using reinforcement learning and state representation learning to improve the efficiency of policy learning. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses using reinforcement learning to control real robots, which falls under the domain of systems and control.
